OL,6,FEight officers are being investigated
OL,7,Fby the police watchdog after a black
OL,8,Fteenager was stopped and searched in
OL,9,FLondon six times in five months.
OL,11,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,12,FConduct said complaints had been made
OL,13,Fby the Haringey Independent Stop and
OL,14,FSearch Monitoring Group on behalf of
OL,15,Fthe 16-year-old and his mother in
OL,16,FApril and June 2023.
