OL,6,FThey related to six incidents where
OL,7,Fthe child was stopped and searched by
OL,8,FMetropolitan Police officers between
OL,9,FJanuary and May of that year across
OL,10,FTottenham and Stratford.
OL,12,FThe IOPC said no further action was
OL,13,Ftaken by officers on each occasion.
OL,15,FThe Met referred itself to the
OL,16,Fregulator in September as part of a
OL,17,Fmandatory complaint referral.
