OL,6,FThe watchdog said grounds provided for
OL,7,Fthe stop-and-search incidents ` four
OL,8,Fof which involved Territorial Support
OL,9,FGroup (TSG) officers and two involving
OL,10,Flocal borough command officers `
OL,11,Fincluded suspicion of drugs or theft,
OL,12,Fand that the child reportedly matched
OL,13,Fdescriptions of people carrying out
OL,14,Frobberies and knife crime in the area.
OL,16,FAs part of its investigation, the IPOC
OL,17,Flooked at officers' body-worn video
OL,18,Ffootage and written records made at
OL,19,Fthe time.
