OL,6,FIOPC director Charmaine Arbouin said:
OL,7,F"The concerning allegations raised in
OL,8,Fthe complaint ` which include racial
OL,9,Fprofiling of a child and insufficient
OL,10,Fgrounds for stopping and searching
OL,11,Fthem six times in five months ` are
OL,12,Fissues that we know disproportionately
OL,13,Faffect black and other minority ethnic
OL,14,Fcommunities and erode public
OL,15,Fconfidence in policing.
