OL,6,F"It's therefore essential that we
OL,7,Fcarry out an investigation `
OL,8,Findependent of the police ` to look at
OL,9,Feach of these incidents and the
OL,10,Factions and decision-making of the
OL,11,Fofficers involved.
OL,13,F"At this stage, we have identified
OL,14,Fpotential conduct issues for eight
OL,15,Fofficers relating to five of these
OL,16,Fincidents. At the end of our
OL,17,Finvestigation, we will make decisions
OL,18,Fon whether any of these officers
OL,19,Fshould face disciplinary proceedings.
